{"tid":1598504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【明報】稱有底線 林鄭：「香港自治」非一國兩制【質疑說漏嘴 學者：一定錯】","createTime":"2019-09-27T13:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:30:59.000Z","uid":251414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55f828fd106a23c6729a914ed5568a99158547e4","tid":1598504,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"2019年9月27日星期五<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190927/s00001/1569523432884/稱有底線-林鄭-「香港自治」非一國兩制\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190927%2Fs00001%2F1569523432884%2F%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%8D%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=51999cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190927%2Fs00001%2F1569523432884%2F%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%8D%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6&h=8e2295e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190927/s00001/1569523432884/稱有底線-林鄭-「香港自治」非一國兩制</a><br />\n稱有底線 林鄭：「香港自治」非一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】昨晚社區對話觸及本港政制問題，有市民表示支持一國兩制，但應跟足《基本法》；有人則擔憂制度變質。有「連登仔」支持實行一國兩制及「香港自治」，特首林鄭月娥回應時強調香港要保持一國兩制，並稱一國兩制有底線，「香港自治就不是一國兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑說漏嘴 學者：一定錯<br />\n中大政治與行政學系高級講師蔡子強形容林鄭月娥猶如「說漏了嘴」，因香港有高度自治，「為何認為『香港自治』就沒有了一國兩制，是否說漏了嘴？現在是否只講全面管治權，不講高度自治，甚至不能說自治？有自治就無一國兩制？」他認為大眾會疑慮是否已收緊香港高度自治，稱這是林太全晚表現「最大敗筆」。</span><br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學公共管治研究部主任李彭廣形容有關說法「一定錯」，疑惑林太是「口誤」或「說漏了嘴」，如非口誤則可能帶出嚴重問題，會令人懷疑香港無高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n市民：唔使多唔使少 跟足基本法<br />\n有市民表示認同一國兩制，「唔使多唔使少」，但必須跟足《基本法》。林鄭月娥回應稱只要確保「準確落實」一國兩制，「香港是有前景的」。其後她重申一國兩制無變質，但一國兩制有底線，呼籲市民尊重，以將熟悉的香港制度保存。<br />\n<br />\n一名26歲「連登仔」發言時向林太推介陳雲的《香港城邦論》，稱書中早已預料本港發生的事，本港面對最大問題是2047、身分問題，因香港回歸50年，年輕人要面對。他說一直感受到中央不斷干預香港，並稱一國兩制不是被港獨破壞，「港獨只是假想敵」，表明自己支持實施一國兩制及香港自治。林太回應時就表明，「香港自治就不是一國兩制」。"},{"pid":"2f6fca597dcfe7da98bab46f50135e6ec1297c00","tid":1598504,"uid":251414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:18:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Genny81437893/status/1177223285316014081?s=08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGenny81437893%2Fstatus%2F1177223285316014081%3Fs%3D08&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=f54a5760\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGenny81437893%2Fstatus%2F1177223285316014081%3Fs%3D08&h=3863775c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Genny81437893/status/1177223285316014081?s=08</a><br />\nGenny Hoffer Sliencer MCIOL<br />\n@Genny81437893<br />\nBreaking: Carrie lam admitted that autonomy is excluded from &quot;one country,  two systems&quot;<br />\n<br />\nHker,  I don't see any reason to give in now.  If you give in,  you lost forever.<br />\nSource:  RTHK<br />\n#chinazi <br />\n#StandwithHK <br />\n#HongKongProtests<br />\n#HongKongProtesters<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xm2Fn89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXm2Fn89.jpg&h=0e99be3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUBZDHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUBZDHw.jpg&h=5d5dce25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvEDUfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvEDUfU.jpg&h=f82e2027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/az4sNAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faz4sNAV.jpg&h=6efb23ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1e3082eadc16a4e56f364f36f64efd34cec8f5f","tid":1598504,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/luipingkuen/posts/1216889025162342 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fluipingkuen%2Fposts%2F1216889025162342%20&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=6cd2925f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/luipingkuen/posts/1216889025162342 </a><br />\n呂秉權<br />\n【高度自治】連新疆、西藏都標榜自己有「自治」，而香港有的更是「高度自治」，在《中英聯合聲明》和《基本法》內保證，列明香港享有「高度自治權」。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥説「香港自治就不是一國兩制」是絕對錯誤，斷送了香港的「高度自治權」，犧牲了700萬港人的前途和利益。林鄭的說法正好反映她替北京蠶食香港的高度自治，出賣港人。<br />\n<br />\n以往在總理的政府工作報告，當對港論述拿走「高度自治」即引起掀然大波，今次由香港行政長官自我矮化，更是嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n圖為《基本法》有關條文<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg12-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71564949_1216889005162344_4768821923847077888_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQk6YXBZba8lq3UiFuhjvUCiD8FRblOaFRm-QPRCbA8KuKaxeNESQo9Kg4eMFfznv3U&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg12-1.fna&amp;oh=2201ff929532bd0adf1a5e7e8ddcb815&amp;oe=5E2F332B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg12-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71564949_1216889005162344_4768821923847077888_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQk6YXBZba8lq3UiFuhjvUCiD8FRblOaFRm-QPRCbA8KuKaxeNESQo9Kg4eMFfznv3U%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg12-1.fna%26oh%3D2201ff929532bd0adf1a5e7e8ddcb815%26oe%3D5E2F332B&h=fec21505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呂秉權<br />\n浸大新聞系高級講師，曾任有線電視中國組首席記者及無綫電視中國組高級記者。十數載的採訪，常遊走中國的天堂與地獄，見證中國的強大與弱小，常念老百姓的血與淚。"},{"pid":"8960652db367307444ffd218b195c42c7c1f36ea","tid":1598504,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"幫林病答埋<br />\n<br />\n我嘅意思係 並非完全自治 只係鳩度自治"},{"pid":"90373f3992dd4595e2f5ccc0e4ea1cce37cc4602","tid":1598504,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"真心講左唔應該講既"},{"pid":"02e5004e571174503f833634b3f7c403c15020a1","tid":1598504,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https:/